"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640274925,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"CEYmOfm_FBw1cw-w8TsPrHxJr6ACwZn2I0PEChF92Ik\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x29bc27d62C76D8Dd0787d720c8407531dA04caC3\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"oIjyxfgQDaM4q1vWwnHmH9Wmb_1tge0JS9XLIve3E_U\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"tB1RBkMp92wMt1writtGzC3ssBa0PLSK8VtLPUABK0o\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"V9lFDYe_liKZkbnvBxz2n0XwLgk_4SIzeEuTX5plUdte1-gMyWKVjA5KVDs51-zk5iao2paqQmOocFzhOXBpkQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xfbb4d3b94f5ccc5db5a73f93a4eae3507d25d9da8489f6ad5fb7db270a5b98020f9777f4dbbd15b7dace547bfa3d8896b36f892a5775f765dd6aede21f3762bd1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"oIjyxfgQDaM4q1vWwnHmH9Wmb_1tge0JS9XLIve3E_U\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"tB1RBkMp92wMt1writtGzC3ssBa0PLSK8VtLPUABK0o\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi